  ... lpfc_sli_issue_mbox_s4+0x533/0x720 [lpfc]
  ... ? mempool_alloc+0x69/0x170
  ... ? dma_generic_alloc_coherent+0x8f/0x140
  ... lpfc_sli_issue_mbox+0xf/0x20 [lpfc]
